      "id": "sybil_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This unit offers a refined driving experience, featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain that ensures long-term dependability. An ideal selection for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of professional sophistication and proven performance.",
