      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved and looked after. It's the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so come take a look and see for yourself how great it drives!",
      "price": 29800.0,
