    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate known chassis fatigue. The engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, and the suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in and minimal body roll. A true driver\u2019s car with high mechanical integrity.",
